subscribers.services.update_email_for_subscriber_by_user(user: accounts.models.CustomUser) → None¶

Update subscriber’s email if User has changed an email, but there was subscriber with ‘previous’ email.

E.g. user has subscribed to the newsletter with email <first@email.com>, then he has changed his email to <second@email.com>, now Subscriber’s email is <second@gmail.com>
